'''''Twilight Falling''''' is the first book in the [[The Erevis Cale Trilogy]] by [[Paul S. Kemp]]. 

{{Quote|''The shadows grow long on the mean streets of [[Selgaunt]]. The sun sets on one man’s service to [[Sembia]]’s merchant lords. The day’s end finds [[Erevis Cale]] serving a [[Mask|new master]], one who is beyond the petty accumulation of wealth.''

''After all, what is gold to one who trades in souls?''}}
